open Kali linux

clone xsstrike repo in tools folder
git clone https://github.com/s0md3v/XSStrike

then change directory to xsstrike by 
cd xsstrike

then install all requirements for the xsstrike by
pip install -r requirements.txt

then use this command for crawling the site by
python3 xsstrike.py -u http://demo.testfire.net/  --crawl -l 4 

then for automation
echo testphp.vulnweb.com | gau | while read url;do python3 xsstrike.py -u $url; done;

https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=4sWkpYKoxCE


